{"tid":1390072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"社會太亂，大家要停一停","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T11:49:37.000Z","uid":279063,"like":134,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"466fc3bab64182b5a71db408e64f26919ff5c240","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:06:35.000Z","msg":"香港呢排好亂，好多事發生。<br />\n<br />\n大家都好不安。<br />\n<br />\n不如放自己一日假，放鬆下心情?<br />\n<br />\n8月5號，請一日假<br />\n<br />\n當係暫停下手頭上嘅工作<br />\n<br />\n俾自己一日喘息嘅空間<br />\n<br />\n#我要和平香港<br />\n#大家靜下來<br />\n#守護香港<br />\n#守護心靈"},{"pid":"fac4393b528b896aeb063d680d7356e52c225aaf","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"哎呀開錯台，陣間開返上班台先"},{"pid":"6ae4d9fda50c413097b6f030c53b5286b9bcf07d","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:13:21.000Z","msg":"點解今次無人搞 保民生 抗修例 路線"},{"pid":"6f0379abb5d109429ca1c81e6d1fe8c34a0e63ef","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"罷工太激進"},{"pid":"31519168c822aed681c170b3a3fa8d4e03083cd6","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:14:17.000Z","msg":"放返日假<br />\n撫平傷口"},{"pid":"397b62885a322b70d9ddf78faec1a828e83f152e","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8f185519df4de965ce4c7f1053443d29c7f80f4","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"不要說推<br />\n試著說<br />\n<br />\n82遮打集會<br />\n85全民罷工"},{"pid":"4bcf85748ef9fd3d86c4997ed31349c7c54f1593","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"用返晒對家啲字眼"},{"pid":"89224713960dc432556b671bf47f4166db50e4f1","tid":1390072,"uid":137721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"睇到標題太衝動禁錯負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067721512c2360fb938949b1c820827dd2d73d52","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"連嗰兩個曲線 page 都無咁樣出 post"},{"pid":"aa153ce91b5b2443c7cbee130f8413ce65c90c29","tid":1390072,"uid":6528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選應要排最頭！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私咁，過埋2047都死左啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"1aa38d072f1384300adc654a2300d190c3189f5d","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89224713960dc432556b671bf47f4166db50e4f1","tid":1390072,"uid":137721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"睇到標題太衝動禁錯負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:17:14.000Z","msg":"幫手推下攞<br />\n<br />\n香港人真係要休息一天<br />\n諗下點行落去"},{"pid":"c52d5d2d89d7db64c29cad9a9029b6125eb01913","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"8月5號<br />\n休息一天"},{"pid":"03da5765bf6a083b19b1e9ef0d190909e515e024","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"8月2號 愛香港，愛和平 遮打集會<br />\n8月5號 全港休息一天"},{"pid":"86a57ae13605ffce46120d5c3238279fb80e8a56","tid":1390072,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"停就輸一世"},{"pid":"89c654c50442d931e67c8bc1aab7d10b20447958","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a57ae13605ffce46120d5c3238279fb80e8a56","tid":1390072,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:22:24.000Z","msg":"停就輸一世"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"sor 我係咪太曲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd69bb54d93ef22f7b9b159bb46fe246a8a584f","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"8月2號 愛香港，愛和平 遮打集會<br />\n8月5號 全港休息一天"},{"pid":"ae31c3984682b0359c868f4b16fc8756272f8935","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:28:43.000Z","msg":"撫平創傷"},{"pid":"b9fa65d8809bbd04cafd1dd0e978f9999c1b609f","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"8月2號 愛香港，愛和平 遮打集會<br />\n8月5號 全港休息一天"},{"pid":"edfdbd08ce460ced7297476f7ab10c42d502f77f","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"8月2號 愛香港，愛和平 遮打集會<br />\n8月5號 全港休息一天"},{"pid":"27699dc0a8ade61361f5dcf69f970d4a3c43dfb8","tid":1390072,"uid":279063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:34:33.000Z","msg":"你啲文宣唔配合返對家字眼，就只係圍爐"},{"pid":"648af593377e97de134857c